-- MOVES-J O Hambro Capital names Bogdan Popescu Europe sales director
-- 
-- Tue Oct 07, 2014 12:49PM EDT
-- None



Oct 7 (Reuters) - UK-based investment management firm J O Hambro Capital Management Ltd appointed Bogdan Popescu as director of European sales, where he will cover French-speaking Europe.

Popescu joins the company from Hilbert Investment Solutions, where he was head of marketing and client services, J O Hambro said.